            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Fortunae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Mogillo<lb break="no" n="3"/>nius Prisc<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>anus pra<lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><abbr>ef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>Raet</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Autopsie R. Wiegels. Bei der Auffindung waren noch Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben erhalten; heute modern mit roter Farbe nachgezogen.</p>
            </div>
